(6663, 4188, 'show_desc', 'EXCLUSIVE SPECIAL\r\n<div class="break"></div>\r\nHow close is today''s technology to catching up with the human body? Two roboticists are on a quest to find out. Follow their mission as they collect the most sophisticated prosthetic parts available and combine them into one single functioning body, complete with an artificial heart, microchip brain, synthetic lungs, kidneys, and even a spleen. Their incredible bionic man reveals just how far science has come and demonstrates where this technology is headed, all the while posing the eternal question of what it means to be human.'),
(6673, 4198, 'show_desc', 'EXCLUSIVE SERIES\r\n<div class="break"></div>\r\nFashion trends are fleeting, but good vintage garments are forever. That''s the philosophy of Doris Raymond, whose West Hollywood clothing store brings vintage glamour to Hollywood''s most influential stylists and costume designers. Follow Doris and her team of "vintage virtuosos" to estate sales, expo shows, and flea markets as they search for vintage gems. Their fabulous finds give designer gowns and fine vintage frocks a second chance to shine in the spotlight at today''s biggest red-carpet events.'),
