(4167, 1, '2013-10-28 17:04:42', '2013-10-28 21:04:42', 'Embark on a stunning journey by air, and through time, to discover the land where settlers'' westward journeys began and Bonnie and Clyde''s crime spree ended. Soar over a frontier rich with the stories of brave pioneers, notorious desperadoes, and hanging judges. Explore the Natural State''s great rivers, great battles and great promise, the birthplace of Johnny Cash, Maya Angelou and Bill Clinton. Join us as we delve into America''s wild interior, from the Mississippi River bottomlands to towering mountain peaks, and into its wild history.', 'Arkansas', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'arkansas', '', '', '2013-10-28 17:04:42', '2013-10-28 21:04:42', '', 4158, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4167', 0, 'page', '', 0),
