(4242, 4, '2013-11-05 14:51:31', '2013-11-05 19:51:31', 'Imagine being aboard a plane with faulty landing gear and watching the drama unfold on the in-flight entertainment system. Or seeing one of your plane''s engines explode mid-flight. When bad things happen on flights, pilots are on their own and passengers have few options other than hoping for the best—and recording the action. See their videos and hear their stories as we investigate near-air disasters caused by faulty equipment, and ask how these incidents could happen aboard today''s state-of-the-art aircrafts.', 'Technical Meltdown', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'technical-meltdown', '', '', '2013-11-05 14:51:31', '2013-11-05 19:51:31', '', 4231, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4242', 0, 'page', '', 0),
