(4250, 4, '2013-11-06 10:47:32', '2013-11-06 15:47:32', 'The history of 20th-century America is on display at Doris Raymond''s vintage clothing boutique, The Way We Wore®. Decades of high fashion from iconic designers fill the racks of this boutique, each telling a story about society at the time. Enter this museum of glamorous garments and discover a treasure trove of memories associated with these pieces, as told by Doris and some of the lively characters who enter her store. If these clothes could talk, their stories would be magnificent.', 'If This Dress Could Talk', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'if-this-dress-could-talk', '', '', '2013-11-12 14:47:14', '2013-11-12 19:47:14', '', 4248, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4250', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4251, 4, '2013-11-06 10:47:09', '2013-11-06 15:47:09', 'The history of 20th-century America is on display at Doris Raymond''s vintage clothing boutique, The Way We Wore(R). Decades of high fashion from iconic designers fill the racks of this boutique, each telling a story about society at the time. Enter this museum of glamorous garments and discover a treasure trove of memories associated with these pieces, as told by Doris and some of the lively characters who enter her store. If these clothes could talk, their stories would be magnificent.', 'If This Dress Could Talk', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4250-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-06 10:47:09', '2013-11-06 15:47:09', '', 4250, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/4250-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4252, 4, '2013-11-06 10:48:18', '2013-11-06 15:48:18', 'Vintage clothing-store owner Doris Raymond is always on the lookout for the "Holy Grail"; the iconic piece that has been touched by one of the world''s greatest designers. During a trip to an expo show in Dallas, she learns of such a garment, discarded at the bottom of a closet. Join the quest as Doris and store manager Sarah Bergman head deep into the heart of Texas. Their hope is to buy this once-in-a-lifetime find, while making a few more vintage purchases along the way.', 'Quest for The Holy Grail', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'quest-for-the-holy-grail', '', '', '2013-11-06 10:48:18', '2013-11-06 15:48:18', '', 4248, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4252', 0, 'page', '', 0),
