(4254, 4, '2013-11-06 10:49:01', '2013-11-06 15:49:01', 'Award season means four months of high-exposure events. It also means four months of madness for the vintage clothing boutique The Way We Wore®. Follow store-owner Doris Raymond and her team as they scout vintage gems for the stylists and the stars. Will the celebs pick Doris'' fabulous pieces? The final whirlwind week leaves Doris and crew watching every step on the red carpet to see if their frocks make a splash on the Hollywood scene.', 'The Awards Season', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-awards-season', '', '', '2013-11-12 14:51:03', '2013-11-12 19:51:03', '', 4248, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4254', 0, 'page', '', 0),
