(4269, 4, '2013-11-06 12:02:03', '2013-11-06 17:02:03', 'Embark on a first-class trip across one of the top vacation destinations in the world, as we explore the grassy waters, sandy shores, and intriguing history of Florida. From big orange groves to Little Havana, from launching rockets to hanging chads, the Sunshine State offers spectacular views and seminal moments that are uniquely its own. Soar over the gleaming metropolis of Miami and the spring break mecca: Panama City. It''s Florida as it''s never been seen before, and you have a window seat!', 'Florida', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'florida', '', '', '2013-11-06 12:02:12', '2013-11-06 17:02:12', '', 4158, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4269', 0, 'page', '', 0),
