(4279, 4, '2013-11-06 14:51:04', '2013-11-06 19:51:04', '"Made in the USA" isn''t just a label. It''s a testament to American ingenuity and a salute to the pioneers and risk takers who have given the world everything from jumbo jets to microchips, ketchup to cornflakes. This all-inclusive, cross-country journey celebrates the nation''s crowning industrial achievements and the people behind them. We soar above Starbucks headquarters, Motown Records, Talladega Superspeedway, and more, exploring America''s stories of inspiration, innovation, and invention.', 'Made In The USA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'made-in-the-usa', '', '', '2013-11-06 14:55:51', '2013-11-06 19:55:51', '', 4158, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4279', 0, 'page', '', 0),
