(4303, 4, '2013-11-06 15:21:59', '2013-11-06 20:21:59', 'North Carolina is home to enduring mysteries, giant industries, and pristine coastal beauty. It''s where gold was first found in America, and where an entire colony of settlers vanished. It''s a state where golf rules the land, NASCAR rules the road, and college basketball holds court over them all. It''s where tobacco became king after the cotton industry went up in smoke, and where a 12-second flight sent shockwaves around the world. Experience the captivating sights and compelling history of one of America''s first colonies.', 'North Carolina', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'north-carolina', '', '', '2013-11-06 15:23:52', '2013-11-06 20:23:52', '', 4158, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4303', 0, 'page', '', 0),
