(4339, 4, '2013-11-06 15:50:23', '2013-11-06 20:50:23', 'The biggest movie and TV franchise of all time, <em>Star Trek</em> spawned more than 700 TV episodes and twelve films. Creator Gene Roddenberry''s vision of the future helped inspire today''s scientists to develop the first scientific principles of teleportation, the creation of artificial intelligence, androids, and more. Now, scientists, series producers, the first Trekkies, and Spock himself, provide new insights into a show that inspired audiences everywhere to create a better world.', 'Star Trek', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'star-trek', '', '', '2013-11-06 15:50:23', '2013-11-06 20:50:23', '', 4329, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4339', 0, 'page', '', 0),
