(4365, 4, '2013-11-06 16:03:53', '2013-11-06 21:03:53', 'Meet the deranged serial killers and the determined FBI agents who inspired one of Hollywood''s most terrifying thrillers and gave Anthony Hopkins and Jodie Foster the roles of a lifetime. We go behind the scenes at the FBI''s Behavioral Science Unit to meet the profilers who became the basis for Harris''s characters and to uncover the details of real-life murderers Ed Gein, Ted Bundy, and others.', 'Silence of the Lambs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'silence-of-the-lambs', '', '', '2013-11-06 16:03:53', '2013-11-06 21:03:53', '', 4329, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4365', 0, 'page', '', 0),
