(4369, 4, '2013-11-06 16:40:11', '2013-11-06 21:40:11', 'Behind Martin Scorsese''s masterful direction and Robert De Niro''s larger-than-life performance lies the very real story of the high-stakes battle between the mob and the law for control of Las Vegas. We interview key figures on both sides of this colorful crime story and detail how the FBI was finally able to overcome the Mafia''s formidable grip on Sin City.', 'Casino', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'casino', '', '', '2013-11-06 16:40:11', '2013-11-06 21:40:11', '', 4329, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4369', 0, 'page', '', 0),
