(4395, 4, '2013-11-07 17:00:25', '2013-11-07 22:00:25', 'Perhaps the scariest part of <em>The Exorcist</em> is that it''s not a work of complete fiction. We recount the 1949 exorcism of a young boy through reenactments and witness accounts. We also show how exorcism continues to this day and how neuroscientists'' recent discoveries dispute this controversial, centuries-old ritual.', 'The Exorcist', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-exorcist', '', '', '2013-11-07 17:00:25', '2013-11-07 22:00:25', '', 4329, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/?page_id=4395', 0, 'page', '', 0),
