(4424, 1, '2014-01-15 10:27:40', '2014-01-15 15:27:40', '<h2>About Smithsonian Channel</h2>\n\n\n<div id="BCLcontainingBlock">\n   <div class="BCLvideoWrapper">\n     <!-- Start of Brightcove Player -->\n     <div style="display:none">\n     </div>\n<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="http://admin.brightcove.com/js/BrightcoveExperiences.js"></script>\n\n<div class="BCLresponsive">\n<object id="myExperience2737936233001" class="BrightcoveExperience">\n  <param name="bgcolor" value="#FFFFFF" />\n  <param name="width" value="100%" />\n  <param name="height" value="530" />\n  <param name="playerID" value="2738088748001" />\n  <param name="playerKey" value="AQ~~,AAAAAF4QYgI~,M7BzSsExP5kEZDbiEtFuyizEVuOO6PDN" />\n  <param name="isVid" value="true" />\n  <param name="isUI" value="true" />\n  <param name="dynamicStreaming" value="true" />\n    <param name="@videoPlayer" value="2737936233001" />\n <!-- params for Universal Player API -->\n                 <param name="includeAPI" value="true" />\n                 <param name="templateLoadHandler" value="onTemplateLoaded" />\n                 <param name="templateReadyHandler" value="onTemplateReady" />\n \n</object>\n</div>\n\n<script type="text/javascript">brightcove.createExperiences();</script>\n\n   </div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Smithsonian Channel is a new commercial-free network in Canada featuring exclusive, award-winning programming that entertains and inspires. Program genres, drawn from the world’s leading cultural institution, include air and space, science and nature, pop culture and history. Smithsonian Channel travels beyond the ordinary to reveal a vast scope of exciting stories and experiences that fuel the curiosity in us all. For more information about the programs you will find on Smithsonian Channel, visit our shows page.</p>\n\n<p>Smithsonian Channel is operated in Canada by Blue Ant Media, the country''s fastest growing media player. To learn more about the company and its other media brands, please visit <a href="http://www.blueantmedia.ca" target="_blank">www.blueantmedia.ca</a></p>\n\n<h2>About Smithsonian Institution</h2>\n\n<p>The Smithsonian Institution consists of 19 museums, the National Zoo, nine research facilities, travelling exhibitions, and more than 150 affiliated museums, making it the world''s largest museum and research complex. The Smithsonian Institution was founded in 1846 by an Act of Congress, signed by US President James K. Polk, with the mission to create an establishment for "the increase and diffusion of knowledge." The scope of the millions of artifacts in the Smithsonian collections is astounding, including everything from Dorothy''s ruby slippers to the Lunar Orbiter. For more information about the Institution, visit the official site.</p>\n\n<h2>Contact</h2>\n\n<p>Smithsonian Channel looks forward to your feedback. Your observations and opinions are important to us. All messages are reviewed and evaluated by our staff, but due to the volume of emails we receive it may take us a few days to respond.</p>\n\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>mailing Address</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col">130 Merton Street, Suite 200<br />\nToronto, ON<br />\nM4S 1A4</div>\n                </div>\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>General information<br />and inquiries</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col"><a href="mailto:feedback@blueantmedia.ca">feedback@blueantmedia.ca</a><br />TEL +1 (416) 646-4431\n<br />FAX +1 (416) 646-4444</div>\n                </div>\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>Website  inquiries</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col">Geoffrey May<br /><a href="mailto:Geoffrey.May@blueantmedia.ca">Geoffrey.May@blueantmedia.ca</a></div>\n                </div>\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>Distribution</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col">Sonja Tessari<br /><a href="mailto:Sonja.Tessari@blueantmedia.ca">Sonja.Tessari@blueantmedia.ca</a></div>\n                </div>\n\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>Publicity / media inquiries</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col">Jennifer Mason<br /><a href="mailto:Jennifer.Mason@blueantmedia.ca">Jennifer.Mason@blueantmedia.ca</a></div>\n                </div>\n\n<div class="about-row">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>Producer inquiries</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col">Marcia Martin<br />\n<a href="mailto:Marcia.Martin@blueantmedia.ca">Marcia.Martin@blueantmedia.ca</a>\n\n<a href="producer-guidelines">Producer Guidelines</a>\n</div>\n                </div>\n\n<div class="about-row-last">\n                    <div class="about-col"><span>Sponsorship sales</span></div>\n                    <div class="about-col-last">Align your brand with premium, high-quality, and credible content sponsorships on Smithsonian Channel. Please contact Anna Carbone at <a href="mailto:anna.carbone@blueantmedia.ca">anna.carbone@blueantmedia.ca</a> to learn more.</div>\n                </div>', 'About & Contact', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4376-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-01-15 10:27:40', '2014-01-15 15:27:40', '', 4376, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/4376-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
