(4498, 4, '2013-11-12 12:58:16', '2013-11-12 17:58:16', 'Burlesque artist Dita von Teese drops by to find the perfect frock for a red-carpet event, while a costume designer from "Glee" shops for the cast''s wardrobe. It''s just another day at the office inside L.A.''s finest vintage store, The Way We Wore®. Meanwhile, store-owner Doris Raymond embarks on a shopping spree at a premiere vintage fashion expo in Santa Monica. See what catches her eye and how she makes the crucial choices that put her store at the forefront of vintage fashion.', 'Vintage Is The New Black', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4261-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-12 12:58:16', '2013-11-12 17:58:16', '', 4261, 'http://staging.smithsonianchannel.ca/4261-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
